.TH "xgmac_poll" 9 "xgmac_poll" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
xgmac_poll \- xgmac poll method (NAPI)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" xgmac_poll
.BI "(struct napi_struct *napi "  ","
.BI "int budget "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "napi" 12
pointer to the napi structure.
.IP "budget" 12
maximum number of packets that the current CPU can receive from
all interfaces.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This function implements the the reception process.
Also it runs the TX completion thread
